title: 1926–27 Scottish Cup
text: The 1926–27 <a href="Scottish%20Cup">Scottish Cup</a> was the 49th season of Scotland's most prestigious <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> knockout competition. The Cup was won by <a href="Celtic%20F.C.">Celtic</a> who defeated <a href="East%20Fife%20F.C.">East Fife</a> in the final at <a href="Hampden%20Park">Hampden Park</a>.
